"https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/configuration/[OpenTelemetry SDK Autoconfigure]\n"
"adding the usual `quarkus.*` prefix."
msgstr "Quarkus 支持 OpenTelemetry 的追踪自动配置功能。这些配置与 link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/configuration/[OpenTelemetry SDK 自动配置中] 显示的内容一致，只是添加了常规的 `quarkus.*` 前缀。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus OpenTelemetry configuration properties now have the `quarkus.otel.*` prefix."
msgstr "Quarkus OpenTelemetry 的配置属性现在都带有 `quarkus.otel.*` 前缀。"

#. type: Plain text
